room_title: Escape room "Intergalactic Express" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: We did the galactic express room and had a lot of fun! The staff was really nice and very helpful. It was a great activity to do with a group of friends! Can't wait to try out another!!

room_title: Escape room "Intergalactic Express" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: We did Intergalactic Express today and immediately upon entering the room, we were amazed at the set design. Everything from start to finish was awesome! We were completely immersed in the game! The puzzles were fun and kept us busy! No escape for us but had a great time! Will be back to try the others :) Thanks Jerry and Kristen!

room_title: Escape room "Intergalactic Express" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: Intergalactic escape was tons of fun, and I don't think we made it through half the clues. Set design was amazing and the clues were well-thought out. Will definitely be going back!

room_title: Escape room "Intergalactic Express" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: The room was a blast, and the staff was so friendly and kind, they made an amazing night out of what started out as a disaster. Definitely gonna go again! We totally died in space, but we got through 70% of it with only three people, so I think we did good lol!
